                     <interp inst="t18060702-26-off135" type="offenceSubcategory" value="grandLarceny"></interp>
               feloniously stealing on the <rs id="t18060702-26-cd136" type="crimeDate">29 of May</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18060702-26-off135 t18060702-26-cd136"></join>, one thousand four hundred pound weight of copper, value 70 l.
            </rs> the property of 
               
                  <persName id="t18060702-26-victim247" type="victimName">
                     Francis 
                     Morgan
